                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420228-1031-offence-1 t18420228-cd-165"></join>31st of December</rs>, 3/4 of a yard of Valentia, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18420228-name-954" type="victimName">
